<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>{خَالِدُونَ <span class="c2">(٣٦)</span>} <span class="c4">[٣٦]</span> تام.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c3">{بِآَيَاتِهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٣٧]</span> حسن، وكاف عند أبي حاتم.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c3">{مِنَ الْكِتَابِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٣٧]</span> حسن، وتام عند نافع.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c3">{يَتَوَفَّوْنَهُمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[٣٧]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لأنَّ <span class="c2">«قالوا»</span> جواب <span class="c2">«إذا»</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
